"""
TypedDI Service Registrations

Comprehensive service registration system using analysis artifacts.
Registers ALL services from analysis/client_map_to_protocol_mapping.json.
Protocol-first registration with concrete class aliasing for production TypedDI.

Key Features:
- Comprehensive registration from analysis/client_map_to_protocol_mapping.json
- Protocol-first registration with concrete class aliasing
- Dynamic import resolution for all service types
- Factory-based dependency resolution from analysis/factory_patterns.json
- Critical service prioritization (DB trio, Slack core)
- Comprehensive error handling and validation

Circular Import Resolution:
- Uses TYPE_CHECKING guards for CompatibilityBridge, TypedResolver, TypedDIContainerAdapter
- Imports these modules lazily within factory functions to avoid module-level circular dependencies
- Factory functions import their dependencies locally to break circular import chains
"""

import inspect
